%section
  .container-fluid.px-0
    .card-group.flex-column.flex-md-row
      #RuggedBox.card.text-white.px-3.px-lg-4.py-4.rounded-0.border-0.mb-0
        .card-body
          %h1.heading.h2.text-white Rugged
          %p.mt-4 Our races are designed to challenge your entire breadth of trail running skills. Big climbs, technical descents, and some of the best scenery you'll find running trails in Texas.
      #WelcomingBox.card.px-3.px-lg-4.py-4.rounded-0.border-0.mb-0
        .card-body
          %h1.heading.h2.text-white Welcoming
          %p.mt-4.text-white We believe that our community is what truly makes us special. From elite speedsters, to back of the pack runners, we have a place for you at our races.
      #FestiveBox.card.text-white.px-3.px-lg-4.py-4.rounded-0.border-0.mb-0
        .card-body
          %h1.heading.h2.text-white Festive
          %p.mt-4 From check-in to crossing the finish line, you will find yourself in a lively, festive atmosphere. Expect fresh pizza, cold beer, and live tunes.
